{"tid":1442611,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢用生果餵飼犬隻","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T10:31:00.000Z","uid":98830,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44bbca3ccd79c9dea15197755b5d43414ad73e97","tid":1442611,"uid":98830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"夢到近排咁多兄弟姊妹叔伯岀街溜狗，小弟見到大家係咁比犬隻攻擊十分心痛，為了略盡棉力。小弟有個奇想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係請這些小犬犬食生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑犬們近日勞累奔波，十分辛苦<br />\n我們要大量購入香蕉火龍果等易爛水果去慰勞佢哋<br />\n(溫馨提示:輕輕將生果壓致微爛, 更易入口)<br />\n拋入狗籠岀入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，既可以餵狗，又可以防止犬隻衡出黎咬人。<br />\n(微爛香蕉及火龍果非一般的滑，滑到其他人就唔好，所以，記住只可以扔係犬隻岀入口)<br />\n不過小心俾人捉到，雖然佢哋只可以告你亂拋垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有唔好拋錯岀街滑到普通人，我地唔可以騷擾到其他人同清潔工人。集中抛係狗籠岀入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想像下香港犬隻柒岀國際，平地都可以仆街，有啲滑潺潺既嘢係地下佢地會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於近日香港警察有點兒思覺失調，人格分裂。會胡亂拘捕人，告人藏有攻擊性武器。就算你車住大量文具觀星雷射筆，佢都可以告你。但係，我車住大量生果，斷估佢都唔會告我掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d345348f64c5dea782f1fcadfccd14ac22d270","tid":1442611,"uid":264192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"火龍果餵食大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3627329a64f051b170b1d49cbd10dd951f3a3d8","tid":1442611,"uid":98830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f4d345348f64c5dea782f1fcadfccd14ac22d270","tid":1442611,"uid":264192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"火龍果餵食大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:16:16.000Z","msg":"記住輕輕壓變咗先餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797b6abe9b9cb0e121b3ccd67bfe1448dd04a604","tid":1442611,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20bf0117c29397357268d8848622f7a8184765fc","tid":1442611,"uid":69289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"下次我用擴音器扮狗叫同班畜牲溝通"},{"pid":"731a370c421fa29dbee2824712dd6d225891c778","tid":1442611,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"著件藍衫，用個西餅盒裝屎。D狗都照收"},{"pid":"e8ce9266a8e692c4504bd8d660e55082f0d6dd62","tid":1442611,"uid":264192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"黑莖一條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcORQPK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcORQPK.png&h=97eb700f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9507e3b8008e19a1acc3f43a3c8c1865735312df","tid":1442611,"uid":98830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"797b6abe9b9cb0e121b3ccd67bfe1448dd04a604","tid":1442611,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44bbca3ccd79c9dea15197755b5d43414ad73e97","tid":1442611,"uid":98830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"夢到近排咁多兄弟姊妹叔伯岀街溜狗，小弟見到大家係咁比犬隻攻擊十分心痛，為了略盡棉力。小弟有個奇想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係請這些小犬犬食生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑犬們近日勞累奔波，十分辛苦<br />\n我們要大量購入香蕉火龍果等易爛水果去慰勞佢哋<br />\n(溫馨提示:輕輕將生果壓致微爛, 更易入口)<br />\n拋入狗籠岀入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，既可以餵狗，又可以防止犬隻衡出黎咬人。<br />\n(微爛香蕉及火龍果非一般的滑，滑到其他人就唔好，所以，記住只可以扔係犬隻岀入口)<br />\n不過小心俾人捉到，雖然佢哋只可以告你亂拋垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有唔好拋錯岀街滑到普通人，我地唔可以騷擾到其他人同清潔工人。集中抛係狗籠岀入口<img src